me.drkapdor.funbazeapi.api.npc.modifier

Class NPCModifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.drkapdor.funbazeapi.api.npc.modifier.NPCModifier
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnimationModifier, EquipmentModifier, LabyModModifier, MetadataModifier, RotationModifier, VisibilityModifier

    public class NPCModifier
extends java.lang.Object
    An NPCModifier queues packets for NPC modification which can then be send to players via the send(Player...) method.
    See Also:
    AnimationModifier, EquipmentModifier, MetadataModifier, RotationModifier, VisibilityModifier, LabyModModifier
